          "rangeStart": 1610,
          "rangeEnd": 2208,
          "markText": "孙子曰：兵者，国之大事￼，死生之地，存亡之道，不可不察也￼",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1715692777,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-05-14 21:19:37",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1610&rangeEnd=2208",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1610&rangeEnd=2208"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_3_520-584",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "520-584",
      "markText": "“后之人，有读（孙）武书予解者，因而学之，犹盘中走丸。丸之走盘，横斜圆直，计于临时，不可尽知；其必可知者，是知丸不能出于盘也。”",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=520&rangeEnd=584",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=520&rangeEnd=584"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_5_7972-8246",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7972-8246",
      "markText": "取用于国，因粮于敌",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7972&rangeEnd=8246",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7972&rangeEnd=8246"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_5_949-956",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "949-956",
      "markText": "兵贵胜，不贵久",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=949&rangeEnd=956",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=949&rangeEnd=956"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_7_3030-3314",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3030-3314",
      "markText": "不可胜在己，可胜在敌",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3030&rangeEnd=3314",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3030&rangeEnd=3314"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_16_1020-1054",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "1020-1054",
      "markText": "先知者，不可取于鬼神，不可象于事，不可验于度，必取于人，知敌之情者也",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1020&rangeEnd=1054",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1020&rangeEnd=1054"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_3_5808-5817",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5808-5817",
      "markText": "以迂为直，以患为利",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5808&rangeEnd=5817",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5808&rangeEnd=5817"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_9_9942-9956",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "9942-9956",
      "markText": "故形人而我无形，则我专而敌分",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=9942&rangeEnd=9956",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=9942&rangeEnd=9956"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_18_423-470",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "423-470",
      "markText": "这本书的作者既懂兵法，又精通《易经》，三十六计几乎每条计都与《易经》有关，有的计还源出《易经》",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=423&rangeEnd=470",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=423&rangeEnd=470"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_3_5473-5522",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5473-5522",
      "markText": "昔之善战者，先为不可胜，以待敌之可胜。不可胜在己，可胜在敌。故善战者，能为不可胜，不能使敌之可胜”",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5473&rangeEnd=5522",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5473&rangeEnd=5522"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_4_427-468",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "427-468",
      "markText": "曹操解释“计”的内涵道：“计者，选将、量敌、度地、料卒、远近、险易，计于庙堂也。”",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=427&rangeEnd=468",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=427&rangeEnd=468"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_4_831-870",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "831-870",
      "markText": "在“五事”的排序中，“道”位居首位，孙子将其界定为：“道者，令民与上同意也。”",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=831&rangeEnd=870",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=831&rangeEnd=870"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_4_9231-9240",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "9231-9240",
      "markText": "势者，因利而制权也",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=9231&rangeEnd=9240",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=9231&rangeEnd=9240"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_6_3369-3411",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3369-3411",
      "markText": "所以，百战百胜，不算是高明之中最高明的；不经交战而使敌人屈服，才是高明之中最高明的。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719939&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3369&rangeEnd=3411",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fe32120718874832fed0c0?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3369&rangeEnd=3411"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719939_14_12872-12938",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "12872-12938",
      "markText": "将士卒置于走投无路的境地，他们就会死战而不会败逃；士卒死战，哪有不得胜之理？士卒人人尽心竭力。一旦士卒深深陷入危险境地，就能团结一心",
